{"tid":262363,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我唔撚想再知屋企d野","createTime":"2017-05-29T07:29:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-29T13:15:13.000Z","uid":32810,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0e4eb2a04384206a38068ea86ecaea4bc65ade51","tid":262363,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:29:12.000Z","msg":"由細到大，老豆老母不停呻窮<br />\n知唔知咁樣搞到我好撚自卑<br />\n我連書都唔撚讀<br />\n就係驚無錢呀<br />\n我唔想再拎你地d零用錢，之後比你西鳩我面<br />\n鬧撚到我喊住返學呀！<br />\n我唔想再返去果d日子<br />\n到我出黎做野<br />\n屋企環境開始好少少<br />\n但心內有條刺<br />\n好驚窮，好驚自己d仔女會同自己一樣<br />\n每日都諗緊錢，每日都聽住父母講自己點樣係窮既情況下養自己<br />\n<br />\n你知唔知我好辛苦？因為你地，我個腦剩係諗錢<br />\n得錢可以比我安全感呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c8762d9474867143db02bbbc5b548166a47707","tid":262363,"uid":32810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:29:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b11d5dfcd93fa72edc8af780cda8648b18e3c0","tid":262363,"uid":109889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:32:06.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />細個父母日日同我講屋企睇窮 乜都買唔起<br />\n依加搞到覺得錢係最重要"},{"pid":"4e518a05c89f32d77dc20b6cd31f41256ca0b238","tid":262363,"uid":11598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:33:05.000Z","msg":"每個月擺低幾K塞住佢哋把口"},{"pid":"c2a133f1ec0ef67bd1469df21aecc22368cf1698","tid":262363,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T07:35:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vignette4.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/0/06/Gdhhd2.gif/revision/latest?cb=20161010061449\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvignette4.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F0%2F06%2FGdhhd2.gif%2Frevision%2Flatest%3Fcb%3D20161010061449&h=25d94161&s={SIZE